author: @givenctdreama1dremakealbum219
text: Renjun is such a gem, there's something very special about his vocals that makes him stand out even in a song with 3 insane technical vocalists. His voice naturally carries so much emotion and his vocal color is very pretty, a bit underrated when we speak about nct as a whole. In the words of vocal coach Sakiko who listed him in his top 5 kpop vocalists "His breathy voice is beautiful and heartbreaking. If you let him sing ballad songs, heâ€™s super strong." Just like in his unbreakable love cover he's always able to share the feeling of the song to the audience, and like in my everything he's perfect for opening songs with his sweet voice, and the contrast of this mellow singing to the strong vocals at the end of rainbow amazes me. I hope we can see more sides of him because there's so much unexplored potential, although he has shown he's very versatile, agile, and has amazing harmonizing skills. As other comments have pointed out, he had no singing background, joined the company as a dancer and trained for a relatively short time, so Huang Renjun you've come a long way, and you are definitely nct's most hidden treasure!
